    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited as a project car or for parts. It has significant high mileage and the exterior shows its age with visible rust on the wheel arches, several large dents, and peeling clear coat. Mechanically, the car needs immediate attention; the engine is running rough, the transmission shifts harshly, and there are multiple fluid leaks. The interior also shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. It is being sold strictly as-is.",
