    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Get ready for a dependable ride that's perfect for your daily commute! This vehicle has served its previous owners well and is ready for more adventures. While it shows some honest cosmetic wear and minor signs of age, it remains a solid, functional choice for anyone looking for great value and reliability on the road.",
