    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Looking for your next great project? This car is ready for a dedicated owner to bring it back to life! While it is currently in poor condition and will require significant repairs and TLC, it remains a fantastic opportunity for a mechanic or hobbyist looking for a budget-friendly start. It\u2019s an honest fixer-upper with plenty of potential for the right person!",
